repnme.cdata!: Egypt - Agricultural and Industrial Imports Project

abstracts.cdata!:
The credit and loan will help finance:
            (i) a portion of the foreign exchange required for the
            import of raw materials, intermediate goods, balancing
            equipment and other inputs to improve utilization of
            existing productive capacities in the agricultural and
            industrial sectors; (ii) the foreign exchange required for
            some urgently needed equipment and spare parts to improve
            the efficiency of operations of the Port of Alexandria; and
            (iii) provision of technical assistance in selected
            sub-sectors of industry.
